      opreq1 fvmpt adantl cn0 0re sylancr adantr simpr w3a eluz2 znn0sub2 sylbi
      ifcl reexpcl syl2anc eqeltrd cc wss uzss 3sstr4g sseld syldan cshi opreq2
      imp zcn nn0ex mptex shftval syl2an 3eqtr4rd seqshft subid seqeq1d opreq1d
      seqfeq 3eqtrd cdiv recnd clt max2 sylancl absid lt01 breq1 ifboth eqbrtrd
      c1 geolim cvv wb seqex a1i climshft syl3anc mpbird breldm ralrimiva fveq2
      wral eleq1d rcla4v sylc abscl cmul wi fveq2d breq12d imbi2d leid breqtrrd
      exp0 eqtrd remulcl eqcomd mulid1 lemul2a ex syl112anc mul12 mulcom eleq2s
      expp1 ax-1cn addsub mp3an2 syl2anr breq2d sylibd peano2uzs cbvralv absge0
      sylib jca max1 lemul1a syl31anc letrd peano2uz letr mpand syld expcom a2d
